Checklist for the time when a new version is about to be released:

1.  check spelling.
2.  check examples.
3.  check documentation on Random* and GraphAttributeStatistics.
4.  check version number
5.  check release date.
6.  check citation info.
7.  remove disclaimer in preface.
8.  build the manual.
9.  clean up backup files.
10. commit changes.
11. push to git repository.
12. push to webpage
    --> git pull, main-master.zip, cheatsheet.pdf, manual.pdf, online manual.
13. update webpage
14. alert on yagsnews@xamanek.izt.uam.mx